content: "The enrollment period for Medicaid never closes. A person can apply for Medicaid coverage through #{Settings.site.short_name} at any time of the year by completing an application for financial assistance. Nothing in this decision impacts the eligibility of anyone in your household who has already been determined eligible for Medicaid or may become eligible in the future."} %>

