content: "If you do not qualify for a new special enrollment period, your next opportunity to enroll in employer-sponsored coverage through #{Settings.site.short_name} is your employer’s annual open enrollment period. You will receive a notification once your annual open enrollment period has begun. This coverage will be effective <strong>#{notice.plan_year.start_on}</strong>."} %>

<%= render partial: 'notices/shared/paragraph', :locals => {
content: "<strong>Individual Market Enrollment</strong>"} %>

<%= render partial: 'notices/shared/paragraph', :locals => {
content: "If you do not qualify to enroll in employer-sponsored coverage or other coverage before then, the annual individual market open enrollment period begins on November 1st of each year. During this period you can enroll in individual market coverage through #{Settings.site.short_name} if you live in the #{Settings.aca.state_name}. If you live outside the #{Settings.aca.state_name}, you can apply during open enrollment through the health insurance exchange operating in your state."} %>

<%= render partial: 'notices/shared/paragraph', :locals => {
content: "There are separate eligibility rules for special enrollment periods into individual market coverage. If you are a #{Settings.aca.state_name} resident and think you might be eligible for an individual market special enrollment period, you can contact #{Settings.site.short_name} to see if you are eligible to enroll through a special enrollment period."} %>

